//*
//*   THE PURPOSE OF THIS PROGRAM IS TO DETECT IF ANY RULES/SETROPTS
//*   SETTING HAVE CHANGED.  THIS WAS WRITTEN DUE TO THE SO CALLED
//*   'SOX' ISSUES MOST COMPANIES HAVE.
//*
//*    THIS PROGRAM ALLOWS YOU TO VERIFY SETROPTS SETTINGS.
//*    THERE ARE 3 TYPES OF INPUT VERIFICATION:
//*   - CLASSES E.G. +SETROPTS CLASSACT=(YYY, ...., )
//*   - FLAGS   E.G. +SETROPTS ERASE=YES,
//*   - CONTENT E.G. +SETROPTS JESNJE=(YES,A???????)
