//* YOU CAN SPECIFY FOR EACH VERIFICATION ONE +SETROPTS ...
//*   STATEMENT OR YOU CAN HAVE ALL VERIFICATION SELECTIONS
//*   IN ONE +SETROPTS STATEMENT.
//*
//*
//*   THE PROGRAM LISTS ALL CURRENT STEROPTS SETTINGS IN //SETROPTS.
//*
//*   MATCHING RULES (+SETROPTS CLASSACT=(... ),ERASE=YES, ETC
//*   WILL BE LISTED UNDER //SETMATCH DD SYSOUT=X.
//*
//*   FAILING RULES (+SETROPTS CLASSACT=(... ),ERASE=YES, ETC
//*   WILL BE LISTED UNDER //SETERROR DD SYSOUT=X.
//*
//*   THE INPUT TO BE PARSED(SO CALLED RULES E.G. +STETROPTS)
//*   WILL BE LISTED UNDER //VERPRINT DD SYSOUT=X.
