//* DATASET RULES RELATED DDNAMES
//* - RACF COMMANDS AND LISTINGS ARE BASED ON USERID-RULE PROCESSING
//*
//DSNPRINT   DD SYSOUT=*   * PRINT DATASETT_RULE CONTROL STATEMENTS
