//* CONNCT RULES RELATED DDNAMES
//* - RACF COMMANDS AND LISTINGS ARE BASED ON USERID-RULE PROCESSING
//*
//CONPRINT   DD SYSOUT=*   * PRINT CONNECT_RULE  CONTROL STATEMENTS
